, tenía 26 años y su mamá, Elizabeth Norton, tenía 22 años. Se casó con Isabel Ogilvy of Auchterhouse, latterly of Bedingfield en 1399, en Bedingfield, Suffolk, Inglaterra, Reino Unido. Fueron padres de por lo menos 1 hijo y 1 hija. Murió el 12 de octubre de 1453, en Northampton, Northamptonshire, Inglaterra, Reino Unido, a la edad de 79 años, y fue sepultado en Northampton, Northamptonshire, Inglaterra."},"sv":{"1374–12 October 1453":"1374–12 oktober 1453","1370–Female":"1370–Avliden","1374–1453":"1374–1453","1377–1410":"1377–1410","1378–1406":"1378–1406","1400–1451":"1400–1451","1402–1454":"1402–1454","1348–1380":"1348–1380","1352–1411":"1352–1411","1 July 1451":"1 juli 1451","1374":"1374","1352":"1352","1451":"1451","1372":"1372","1382":"1382","1370":"1370","1380":"1380","1348":"1348","1402":"1402","12 October 1453":"12 oktober 1453","1400":"1400","1411":"1411","1378":"1378","1399":"1399","1454":"1454","1410":"1410","1377":"1377","1453":"1453","1406":"1406","Northampton, Northamptonshire, England":"Northampton, Northamptonshire, England","Denham St Mary, Suffolk, England":"Denham St Mary, Suffolk, England","Oxborough, Norfolk, England":"Oxborough, Norfolk, England","Bedingfield, Suffolk, England":"Bedingfield, Suffolk, England"},"tl":{"1374–12 October 1453":"1374–ika–12 ng Oktubre 1453","1370–Female":"1370–Patay Na","1374–1453":"1374–1453","1377–1410":"1377–1410","1378–1406":"1378–1406","1400–1451":"1400–1451","1402–1454":"1402–1454","1348–1380":"1348–1380","1352–1411":"1352–1411","1 July 1451":"ika-1 ng Hulyo 1451","1374":"1374","1352":"1352","1451":"1451","1372":"1372","1382":"1382","1370":"1370","1380":"1380","1348":"1348","1402":"1402","12 October 1453":"ika-12 ng Oktubre 1453","1400":"1400","1411":"1411","1378":"1378","1399":"1399","1454":"1454","1410":"1410","1377":"1377","1453":"1453","1406":"1406","Northampton, Northamptonshire, England":"Northampton, Northamptonshire, England","Denham St Mary, Suffolk, England":"Denham St Mary, Suffolk, England","Oxborou